escription":"\u003cp\u003eBring home one of cinema’s most iconic moments with this 3-piece split poster inspired by *The Shawshank Redemption*. The warm glowing tones, powerful silhouette and the quote “Hope can set you free, but fear can hold you prisoner” create a bold and emotional centrepiece for any room.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePrinted on premium 300 GSM matte photo paper, each panel delivers rich colours, sharp details and a smooth anti-glare finish. The 3-piece split layout adds depth and presence, making it perfect for bedrooms, studios, offices or cinematic room setups.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA must-have for movie lovers, motivational art fans and anyone who connects with the timeless message of hope, freedom and resilience.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394462712104,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394462744872,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394462777640,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/w_c65b7809-0e81-47c6-b63c-92af62939004.webp?v=1763209508"}],"url":"https:\/\/www.posterized.in\/collections\/f1-split-collections.oembed","provider":"Posterized","version":"1.0","type":"link"}